{{Item infobox | description = Double-click to open. | icon = Trick-or-Treat Bag.png | rarity = basic | type = container | bound = acquire | id = 48793, 48795 | status = historical | status notes = Only available during [[Blood and Madness 2013|Blood and Madness 2013]] and [[Blood and Madness 2014|Blood and Madness 2014]]. }} [[Bag of Confiscated Treats]] is a reward for completing [[Resealing the Bloody Prince]] during [[Blood and Madness 2013|Blood and Madness]].
== Halloween 2014 == === Acquisition === {{rewarded by}}
=== Contents === * Random piece of [[equipment]] of your character's [[Character#Progression|level]] with {{rarity|masterwork}} [[Item#Rarity|rarity]] or above. * {{contains|Trick-or-Treat Bags|qty=5|notes=In 2014|chance=Guaranteed}}
== Halloween 2013 == === Acquisition === * Completing [[Resealing the Bloody Prince]] for the first time per day.
=== Contents === * Random chance for about {{coin|75}} * Two random [[weapon]]s or pieces of [[armor]] with masterwork [[Item#Rarity|rarity]] or above. * {{contains|Large Candy Bag|qty=5|chance=Guaranteed}}
=== Rare version === Players have a very rare chance to receive a different bag of the same name (They don't stack) containing: * {{contains|Candy Corn Cob|chance=Guaranteed}} * {{contains|Gibbering Skull|qty=5|chance=Guaranteed}} * {{contains|High-Quality Plastic Fangs|qty=5|chance=Guaranteed}} * {{contains|Tyria's Best Nougat Center|qty=5|chance=Guaranteed}}
